data.description: Welcome to this 3 bedroom 2 bathroom single story which is convenient to everything Summerville has to offer!  From the foyer into the family room with vaulted ceiling and wood burning fireplace.  The open living space flows effortlessly to the kitchen and dining area, or out to the covered patio in the fenced back yard.    The large primary suite, complete with tray ceiling, dual vanity, jetted tub and separate shower is on the rear of the home.  The ample secondary bedrooms share the additional bath.  With no carpeting, fenced yard this home is ready for you to enjoy.
